{"id":"586907fa-8b05-e1eb-aab6-23f722f0b2e6","Content":[{"Language":"nl-NL","Content":"[$BOX]\n\t[$CELL]\n\t\t[$BLOCK]\n\n\t\t\t<h3>Het toedienen van medicijnen met behulp van een droogpoederinhalator (DPI)</h3>\n\t\t\t<table class=\"table-excel-borders\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n\t\t\t\t<tbody align = \"left\" valign = \"top\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr valign=\"top\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th align=\"left\" width=\"50%\">Handeling: Het toedienen van inhalatiemedicijnen met behulp van een droogpoederinhalator (DPI)</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th width=\"10%\">N.v.t</th>\n                        <th width=\"10%\">Goed</th>\n                        <th width=\"10%\">Kan beter</th>\n                        <th width=\"10%\">Fout</th>\n                        <th width=\"10%\">Niet gedaan</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td><strong>1. Verzamelt de benodigdheden:</strong></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1.1 Toedienlijst</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1.2 Droogpoederinhalator met medicijn (inclusief gebruiksinstructie)</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1.3 Eventuele inhalatiecapsule(s)</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1.4 Wegwerpbekken</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1.5 Tissue</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1.6 Glas water</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td><strong>2. Bereidt zich adequaat voor:</strong></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2.1 Past handhygiëne toe.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2.2 Zet de benodigdheden klaar op een schoon werkveld.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2.3 Regelt een dubbele controle van de medicatie.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2.4 Controleert de identiteit van de zorgvrager (naam en geboortedatum).</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2.5 Controleert het medicijn (naam, soort, dosis, houdbaarheidsdatum, kleur, uiterlijk, toedieningswijze).</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2.6 Vergelijkt het medicijn met de toedienlijst.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2.7 Geeft de zorgvrager instructies en informatie over de medicatie en toediening.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td><strong>3. Voert de handeling uit:</strong></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n                  \t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.1 Helpt de zorgvrager in de juiste houding (rechtop zittend of staand, met het hoofd iets naar achteren gebogen).</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.2 Controleert of de mond van de zorgvrager leeg is (geeft eventueel een slok water bij een droge mond).</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.3 Maakt de poederinhalator gebruiksklaar volgens de instructies.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.4 Laat de zorgvrager langzaam en volledig uitademen.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.5 Instrueert de zorgvrager om het mondstuk tussen de tanden te nemen en de lippen eromheen te sluiten, terwijl de inhalator horizontaal wordt gehouden.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.6 Laat de zorgvrager diep, krachtig en gelijkmatig inademen.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.7 Neemt de inhalator uit de mond van de zorgvrager.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.8 Instrueert de zorgvrager de adem 10 seconden in te houden en daarna rustig door de neus uit te ademen.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.9 Herhaalt de procedure vanaf stap 3.4 indien een tweede dosis is voorgeschreven.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.10 Laat na de laatste inhalatie de mond en keel spoelen met water (eerste slok spoelen en uitspugen, tweede doorslikken) of iets eten/drinken.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.11 Wacht bij het gebruik van meerdere inhalatiemedicijnen 1 minuut voor het inhaleren van het volgende medicijn.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.12 Verwijdert de eventuele lege capsule en sluit de poederinhalator door de beschermkap terug te plaatsen.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-oddrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.13 Reinigt het mondstuk met een droge tissue en spoelt het mondstuk niet af.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td><strong>4. Rondt de handeling af:</strong></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>4.1 Ruimt de materialen op.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>4.2 Past handhygiëne toe.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr class=\"table-excel-evenrow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>4.3 Tekent de toedienlijst af en noteert de relevante gegevens (o.a. tijdstip, soort medicijn, hoeveelheid, bijzonderheden).</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&square;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t</table>\n\n\t\t[$/BLOCK]\n\t[$/CELL]\n[$/BOX]","Name":"Het toedienen van medicijnen met behulp van een droogpoederinhalator (DPI)"}]}